FBIS4-38299 "drnes126_j_94011" FBIS-NES-94-126 Daily Report 30 Jun 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Paper Says al-Bid Sought Refuge in Saudi Arabia Paper Says al-Bid Sought Refuge in Saudi Arabia JN3006075794 Amman AKHBAR AL-USBU' in Arabic 30 Jun 94 pp 1, 18 JN3006075794 Amman AKHBAR AL-USBU' Arabic BFN [Excerpt] Sanaa, Aden -- [South Yemeni leader] 'Ali Salim al-Bid yesterday sought refuge in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia after fleeing from al-Mukalla and abandoning Aden, which was fully paralyzed by the intensive shelling from all directions by the government forces. [passage omitted]
